# EZ Dating Child Safety Standards

Effective date: February 12, 2026

EZ Dating is intended for adults only. We do not permit use by anyone under 18. We are committed to preventing, detecting, and reporting child sexual abuse and exploitation (CSAE) and any content or behavior that harms minors.

## Our Standards
- Prohibit any content, behavior, or solicitation involving minors or CSAE.
- Use age restrictions and require users to confirm they are 18 or older.
- Provide in-app reporting and account blocking tools.
- Take immediate action on reports of suspected CSAE, including removal of content and account bans.
- Preserve and report relevant information to appropriate authorities and the National Center for Missing and Exploited Children (NCMEC) or equivalent organizations, as required by law.

## Reporting
Users can report safety concerns or suspected CSAE from within the app and by emailing:
- shashankbasrur@gmail.com

We review reports promptly and may request additional information to investigate.

## Enforcement
We may remove content, suspend, or permanently ban accounts that violate these standards. We also cooperate with law enforcement when required.

## Contact
If you have questions about these standards, contact:
shashankbasrur@gmail.com
